<Window
    x:Class="OVR_Dash_Manager.Forms.Profile_Manager.ProfileManagerHelp"
    xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
    xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
    xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
    xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
    Title="Profile Manager Help"
    Width="800"
    Height="450"
    Background="#FF040404"
    Foreground="White"
    mc:Ignorable="d">
    <Grid>
        <ScrollViewer VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Auto">
            <TextBlock Padding="10" TextWrapping="Wrap">
                <Bold>Profile Manager: Streamlined Script Execution for Enhanced VR Experience</Bold>
                <LineBreak />
                <LineBreak />
                Welcome to the Profile Manager, a powerful feature designed to elevate your virtual reality (VR) experience. With a focus on efficiency and user convenience, the Profile Manager seamlessly integrates scripts hosted on GitHub, ensuring that you always have access to the latest enhancements and configurations.<LineBreak />
                <LineBreak />
                <Bold>🔹 Quick Access to Scripts:</Bold>
                <LineBreak />
                The Profile Manager effortlessly fetches scripts from a dedicated GitHub repository, ensuring that you are always up-to-date with the latest developments and optimizations.<LineBreak />
                <LineBreak />
                <Bold>🔹 Temporary File Handling:</Bold>
                <LineBreak />
                Scripts are securely downloaded to a temporary file. This approach ensures that your system remains clutter-free, and you always execute the most recent version of the script.<LineBreak />
                <LineBreak />
                <Bold>🔹 One-Click Execution:</Bold>
                <LineBreak />
                Experience the simplicity of executing scripts with just a double-click. The scripts are meticulously processed through the OculusDebugToolCLI.exe, ensuring accurate and reliable application of configurations and enhancements.<LineBreak />
                <LineBreak />
                <Bold>🔹 Enhanced VR Experience:</Bold>
                <LineBreak />
                By leveraging the Profile Manager, you empower yourself with optimized configurations and enhancements that aim to improve the performance and quality of your VR sessions.<LineBreak />
                <LineBreak />
                <Bold>🔹 Contribute Your Scripts:</Bold>
                <LineBreak />
                If you wish to contribute your own scripts or explore the existing ones, feel free to visit our GitHub repository:<Hyperlink
                           Foreground="DodgerBlue"
                           NavigateUri="https://github.com/DevOculus-Meta-Quest/OVRDM-Profile-Scripts"
                           RequestNavigate="Hyperlink_RequestNavigate">
                    OVRDM-Profile-Scripts
                </Hyperlink>
                . You can create pull requests to add your own scripts if you wish to contribute.
            Utilize the Profile Manager to effortlessly apply sophisticated scripts, optimize your settings, and immerse yourself in a refined and enriched virtual reality experience.</TextBlock>
        </ScrollViewer>
    </Grid>
</Window>